&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate will have 10–15 years of enterprise B2B field marketing experience, a track record of delivering measurable impact, and the ability to move quickly from strategic planning to tactical execution. Experience supporting multiple geographic and segment territories simultaneously is essential.&lt;/p&gt;
