&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Background in accounting, finance, or CPA certification with understanding of GAAP/IFRS reporting requirements&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Experience with Workday Accounting Center for complex journal automation and subledger accounting&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Technical proficiency with SQL, Python, or scripting languages for data analysis and integration support&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Experience integrating Workday with external data platforms such as BigQuery or cloud data warehouses&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Knowledge of SOX compliance requirements and internal controls for financial systems&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
